code":"separators","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" arguments, those","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"variables must thus outlive the iterator and not be modified during the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"iteration."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"wwwForm","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is passed in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"flags"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"+"},{"text":" characters in the param","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"string will be replaced with spaces in the output. For example, ","type":"text"},{"code":"foo=bar+baz","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"will give attribute ","type":"text"},{"code":"foo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"bar baz"},{"type":"text","text":". This is commonly used on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"web (the "},{"code":"https","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"http"},{"text":" schemes only), but is deprecated in favour of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the equivalent of encoding spaces as "},{"code":"20","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unlike with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_uri_parse_params()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"caseInsensitive"},{"type":"text","text":" has no"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"effect if passed to "},{"code":"flags","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"code":"g_uri_params_iter_init()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". The caller is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"responsible for doing their own case-insensitive comparisons."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):"